creator: Camile Thai
descriptionHtml:
Place an order from your nearest store for delivery or collection and enjoy the healthiest Thai delivery in town, delivered to you fast.

Ordering is quick, easy and secure. Log in with your Camile account or create one in seconds. Reorder the dishes you love fast by adding them to your favorites list.

FEATURES:

- The lowest prices available on our Thai delivery, both in-store and online

- Exclusive app-only offers

- Explore our menu easily and super fast

- Vegan options separated for simpler ordering

- Full allergen information available on each dish

Find us on FB (facebook.com/CamileThaiIreland) (facebook.com/CamileThaiUK)

Instagram (camilethaiirl)(camilethaiuk)

Twitter (@camilethaiirl) (camilethaiuk)

Or drop us a line at info@camile.co.uk.
